Revision history for Tree-Authz

0.03    21 Aug 2005, 01:45
    - no change, been using for ages without problems

0.02_2   2 Dec 2004, 22:22 GMT
    - removed a couple of tests of the database API, which is still
      very experimental. 

0.02_1  30 Nov 2004, 17:00 GMT
    - changed terminology to talk about 'roles' instead of 'groups'
    - renamed some methods to reflect new terminology
    - old methods should still work, but will complain via carp
    - added a new class to represent roles - Tree::Authz::Role

0.01    Date/time
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

